#: ../../faq.rst:784
# fb5bf583d6524593bf6c7b2a6eb45635
msgid "You are using a Wacom branded USB mouse. There is an incompatibility between Wacom mice and the graphics toolkit |app| uses. Try using a non-Wacom mouse."
