# fd5d9a4c04604323868c2bba7f50d5ef
msgid "My antivirus program claims |app| is a virus/trojan?"
msgstr ""

#: ../../faq.rst:878
# 56b1412b9a5743b5b2206c6c74d38c72
msgid "The first thing to check is that you are downloading |app| from the official website: `<http://calibre-ebook.com/download>`_. Make sure you are clicking the download links on the left, not the advertisements on the right. |app| is a very popular program and unscrupulous people try to setup websites offering it for download to fool the unwary."
