#: ../../faq.rst:899
# 9c0a4de96b2e47eda685ec3e988092a1
msgid "You can switch |app| to using a backed up library folder by simply clicking the |app| icon on the toolbar and choosing your backup library folder. A backed up library folder backs up your custom columns and saved searches as well as all your books and metadata."
